that we got her.

772
00:28:40,302 --> 00:28:41,971
Huntley and Brinkley
are humiliated.

773
00:28:42,054 --> 00:28:43,597
Oh, God, that makes me so happy.

774
00:28:43,681 --> 00:28:45,641
