Maybe a nickel.

778
00:28:52,815 --> 00:28:54,191
Keep the change, please.

779
00:28:56,819 --> 00:28:57,819
Hello.

780
00:28:57,820 --> 00:28:59,780
Oh. Hello.

781
00:28:59,864 --> 00:29:01,657
- I'm Hedy Ford.
- I know.

782
00:29:01,740 --> 00:29:03,020
